{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDI2MjQ1MTY1", "number": 1002, "title": "HDDS-3642. Stop/Pause Background services while replacing OM DB with checkpoint from Leader", "bodyText": "What changes were proposed in this pull request?\nWhen a follower OM needs to replace its DB with a checkpoint from Leader (to catch up on the transactions), it should pause or stop services which read/ write to the DB.\nDuring OM HA testing, found that OM could crash with JVM error on RocksDB. This happened because KeyDeletingService was trying to access a memory which is already freed up.\nPlease see Jira link below for error logs.\nWhat is the link to the Apache JIRA\nhttps://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HDDS-3642\nHow was this patch tested?\nTested on a local docker cluster.", "createdAt": "2020-06-01T22:21:45Z", "url": "https://github.com/apache/ozone/pull/1002", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "aa04ac0a894e15c98b05b1acef110c6e26bb01dc"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-06-14T07:49:01Z", "author": {"login": "hanishakoneru"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 7, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcpVtXUABqjM0MjE2OTE0MDc=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcqm3cNgFqTQyOTk0MTk2Mg==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "HeadRefForcePushedEvent", "beforeCommit": {"oid": "98654eabfbb807fc55a772eb631b3ead4e5bccf5", "author": {"user": {"login": "hanishakoneru", "name": "Hanisha Koneru"}}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/ozone/commit/98654eabfbb807fc55a772eb631b3ead4e5bccf5", "committedDate": "2020-06-01T22:19:05Z", "message": "HDDS-3642. Stop/Pause Background services while replacing OM DB with checkpoint from Leader"}, "afterCommit": {"oid": "f1c4a27e1560401d9cb3561adc627360588f801c", "author": {"user": {"login": "hanishakoneru", "name": "Hanisha Koneru"}}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/ozone/commit/f1c4a27e1560401d9cb3561adc627360588f801c", "committedDate": "2020-06-08T19:34:08Z", "message": "HDDS-3642. Stop/Pause Background services while replacing OM DB with checkpoint from Leader"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDI2NTU4NjA5", "url": "https://github.com/apache/ozone/pull/1002#pullrequestreview-426558609", "createdAt": "2020-06-08T19:33:57Z", "commit": {"oid": "98654eabfbb807fc55a772eb631b3ead4e5bccf5"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNi0wOFQxOTozMzo1N1rOGgtepw==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNi0wOFQxOTozMzo1N1rOGgtepw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQzNjk1Mjc0Mw==", "bodyText": "Right now, we don't have any stop() for S3SecretManager and PrefixManager.\nAnd also for these, only read/write operations will happen. Write will go through double buffer and read's will not happen anyway as this is not leader. Do we still see issue?", "url": "https://github.com/apache/ozone/pull/1002#discussion_r436952743", "createdAt": "2020-06-08T19:33:57Z", "author": {"login": "bharatviswa504"}, "path": "hadoop-ozone/ozone-manager/src/main/java/org/apache/hadoop/ozone/om/OzoneManager.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -3113,27 +3120,32 @@ private DBCheckpoint getDBCheckpointFromLeader(String leaderId) {\n     return null;\n   }\n \n+  void stopServices() throws Exception {\n+    keyManager.stop();\n+    stopSecretManager();\n+    metadataManager.stop();\n+\n+    // s3SecretManager should also be stopped", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "98654eabfbb807fc55a772eb631b3ead4e5bccf5"}, "originalPosition": 44}]}}, {"__typename": "HeadRefForcePushedEvent", "beforeCommit": {"oid": "f1c4a27e1560401d9cb3561adc627360588f801c", "author": {"user": {"login": "hanishakoneru", "name": "Hanisha Koneru"}}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/ozone/commit/f1c4a27e1560401d9cb3561adc627360588f801c", "committedDate": "2020-06-08T19:34:08Z", "message": "HDDS-3642. Stop/Pa